{"tid":102722,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打同我一樣好驚搭巴士有女仔坐隔離?","createTime":"2017-01-31T20:50:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-03T11:28:44.000Z","uid":71008,"like":3,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e7987598f902644e4f1b3f886ec89eadbd9a0251","tid":102722,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T20:50:48.000Z","msg":"頭先我搭巴士去信和，坐下層座位。一開始隔離都係d買餸c9，咁我都冇咩驚。點知搭搭下d c9 阿叔落曬車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，上左幾個後生嘅女仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，仲幾靚幾潮(有個仲染到頭髮銀色，著條爛褲腳嘅牛仔褲，同我地屋邨d c9差好遠)。 佢地見冇位坐就坐曬我隔離。我即刻勁驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而且佢地幾個好似係friend，一路有講有笑，d聲音畫面搞到我仲加勁緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，成個身硬曬，頭都唔敢轉，好似俾人打把咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，流左好多汗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n後嚟我到左站都唔敢落車，因為我坐窗邊個位，要落車佢地就要讓開(而且係好開，我好肥)，我唔夠膽開聲問佢地可唔可以俾我落<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，最後搭左去尖東佢地落車我先夠膽落車。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4715b5294d35d2c0385e9be1c503d72b5c55707e","tid":102722,"uid":53775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T20:52:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />驚乜撚<br />\n驚佢強姦你咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50b53893141f9dfb84c49f40a7ab57eb6478fdc3","tid":102722,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T20:54:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />驚乜撚<br />\n驚佢強姦你咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我見到後生嘅女仔就好緊張 講嘢都唔正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"